titles.title: To grant a Federal charter to the National American Indian Veterans, Incorporated.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on the Judiciary.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Immigration, Citizenship, Refugees, Border Security, and International Law.

bill.summary:
1/23/2007--Introduced.
Grants a Federal charter to the National American Indian Veterans, Incorporated (a nonprofit corporation organized in the United States).
